### ssh config

IgnoreUnknown GSSAPIRenewalForcesRekey,UpdateHostKeys

Host github.com

    User mustangflyer

Host *

    # session reuse
    ControlMaster auto
    ControlPath ~/.local/run-user-dir/ssh_%r@%h_port%p

    # session meta
    Compression yes
    EscapeChar ^~
    Protocol 2

    # hosts
    HashKnownHosts yes
    UpdateHostKeys ask

    # auth
    PasswordAuthentication   no
    GSSAPIAuthentication     yes
    GSSAPIRenewalForcesRekey yes

    #Â ssh keys on per-host basis
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/keys/%h.key
